subject: Send "Show" signal if application resumes with "tizen.application.launch"
commitMessage:
Send "Show" signal if application resumes with "tizen.application.launch"

If an application is launched with "tizen.application.launch", we now
verify if it is already running ; if it is, we wend a new "Show" D-Bus
signal to it. This signal will be catched by Crosswalk.

Bug-Tizen: TC-1352

Change-Id: I7bc256b63750ef49f25f1be5b841ad2ea5be5394
Signed-off-by: Manuel Bachmann <manuel.bachmann@open.eurogiciel.org>
